body:
This is curious.
Maybe there are two different versions of protoc?
This message looks interesting to me
```
This file was generated by a newer version of protoc which is incompatible with your Protocol Buffer headers. Please update your headers.
```

Where did you download protobuf packages you installed?

@jhseu in case he can help.
